channel.title: How to make an invisible folder
channel.description:
Well.. To start of the tutorial
Right click on the desktop.
Go to "New"
Then click "Folder"
Now you have to pick a name just hold ALT and press 0160
Then press enter Now the folder has no name..
Still not invisible though ..Go to properties..
"Customize" > "Change Icon"
Then scroll a little to right and find a icon that has no well icon.. [img]http://img524.imageshack.us/img524/9278/invisible1dc4.png[/img]
Now that folder is invisible :D
[IMG]http://img444.imageshack.us/img444/4116/invisible2hh2.png[/img]
____________________________
Now you can hide your stack of porn :D ______________________________________
What if you want 2 folders in your desktop?
Well then when your typing in the same just hold ALT and press 0160 2 times
